call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Replay review of the OOB called on Conley Jr. (UTA) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Jones (NOP) touches the ball last before it goes OOB.
Nance Jr. (NOP) slightly extends his right forearm towards Olynyk's (UTA) back during pursuit of the rebound, and Olynyk draws attention to the marginal contact.
Murphy III (NOP) moves alongside Clarkson?s (UTA) path before absorbing contact as Clarkson elevates for the driving shot attempt, and marginal body contact occurs.
Vanderbilt (UTA) and Nance Jr. (NOP) engage and disengage off-ball as Nance Jr. establishes position to receive the entry pass, and marginal contact occurs.
Alvarado (NOP) establishes screening position in Clarkson's (UTA) path before slightly rotating his backside, but the two avoid making contact.
Clarkson (UTA) brushes McCollum's (NOP) back during the follow-through of his jump shot attempt, and marginal contact occurs.
Clarkson (NOP) extends his right leg out during the follow-through of his jump shot attempt but avoids contact with McCollum (NOP) contesting the shot.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: McCollum (NOP) touches the ball last before it goes OOB.
Murphy III (NOP) initiates contact to Clarkson?s (UTA) front that affects his SQBR during the drive.
Clarkson (UTA) slides his right foot that is his pivot foot to gain separation from McCollum (NOP) for his shot attempt.
Nance Jr.'s (NOP) off-arm comes down slightly onto Markkanen's (UTA) left arm as the former elevates for the shot attempt at the basket, and marginal contact occurs.

Murphy III (NOP) defend Markkanen (UTA) drive with a resting hand along his side, Markkanen gathers the ball and wedges Murphy's arm between his arm and side. The shot occurs without Murphy grabbing or catching the shooters arm.
McCollum (NOP) brings his off-arm toward Markkanen?s (UTA) side and marginal contact occurs as he attempts to dribble around Markkanen during the drive.
Olynyk (UTA) touches the ball last before it goes OOB.
Jones (NOP) applies an arm to Markkanen?s (UTA) front that affects his SQBR during the drive.
Valanciunas (NOP) and OIynyk (UTA) engage and disengage during the free throw attempt by Markkanen (UTA), and Olynyk draws attention to the marginal contact.
Valanciunas (NOP) steps into the lane before stepping back out prior to the release of Markkanen's (UTA) free throw attempt.
Olynyk (UTA) momentarily loses control of the ball before gathering it and taking two legal steps for the driving shot attempt.
McCollum (NOP) moves alongside Olynyk?s (UTA) path before coming slightly forward, and Olynyk moves through the marginal body contact during the driving shot attempt.
Inconclusive. McCollum (NOP) remains in-bound while moving up the sideline on the final possession.
